readme: # react-native-star-view [![Build Status](https://travis-ci.org/FaiChou/react-native-star-view.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/FaiChou/react-native-star-view) ![license](https://img.shields.io/github/license/mashape/apistatus.svg) ### How to use Install package: ``` npm install --save react-native-star-view # or yarn add react-native-star-view ``` Import to your app: ``` import Star from 'react-native-star-view'; ``` Use the component: ``` render() { const starStyle = { width: 100, height: 20, marginBottom: 20, }; return ( ); } ``` ### API API name | Desc ---------------|---------------------------------------- score | score number, Required totalScore | total score, default is 5, Optional style | style of container, Optional
